txt.en: 'The Lumber-mill is ready for the woodcutters and workers to move in and begin cutting the lumber into boards that we can use to repair and rebuild the palisades and buildings of Hytbold. None of that can happen without the workers, though. It is time we send out a call across the Eastemnet and get this mill fully up and running.'
'Hytbold is one step closer to being rebuilt and restored.'
There is much work to do to rebuild the town of Hytbold.
